<object type="traktor.mcp.SkillAsset">
	<name>traktor-lua-scripting</name>
	<description>Idioms and gotchas for authoring traktor LUA Stage scripts (namespace import, direct type references, #using, Stage lifecycle).</description>
	<whenToUse><![CDATA[Writing or editing a LUA Stage/script in traktor (e.g. Scripts/Main), or wiring entity/component logic from script.]]></whenToUse>
	<body><![CDATA[# Authoring traktor LUA scripts

Conventions and gotchas for writing a LUA `Stage` script (e.g. `Scripts/Main`). These are style/idiom rules, not a task — apply them whenever you author or edit a script.]]></body>
	<engineVersion/>
	<published>true</published>
	<parameters/>
</object>
